Text: Exactly :( like my choices are worry people, be forced to eat, or lie so I have to lie

Author: sugokunai
Text: S A M E oh my gosh, lying is usually so painful for me but when it comes to covering up my ED habits it just comes right out so easily and it makes me feel so weird and bad but like I have no choice if I want other people not to worry..
